{"tid":1781594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六有野做：全民運動","createTime":"2019-12-13T09:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T07:43:43.000Z","uid":23758,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5b230ea3ae3a203cb872d5957b28d921beff4a77","tid":1781594,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"你地休息緊既時候，黑警係到戴住豬嘴練體能<br />\n半年時間唔知有幾多隻散仔練到速龍咁<br />\n對方不停升緊級<br />\n香港人就淨係識傾周末冇遊行集會去邊到玩好<br />\n<br />\n香港人既體能本身就好唔夠，跑得又慢又短<br />\n上得前線既人又不斷減少緊<br />\n咁點樣先可以夠班黑警打<br />\n特別係冬天又會懶得郁，體能只會更差<br />\n<br />\n如果冇活動，就自發約人做運動<br />\n塞爆健身室，塞爆康文署，塞爆球場<br />\n冇波打就玩捉依因<br />\n冇位就跑步<br />\n實搵到地方比你練好體能<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想場運動就咁完，想持續到贏為止<br />\n就唔好放鬆，試下自發咁搵野做<br />\n煲底見"},{"pid":"ecf0028db0b20d5faaf313d39f3b5bcd08be326d","tid":1781594,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"783c4820622a0449fba69d10b7425d9246d72b41","tid":1781594,"uid":7168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"想係商場玩捉依因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ecae28f492494bc636609543dda0127eb4c013","tid":1781594,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:52:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"727bd2a8f29dc79814bd4d0c886096b0afa931b6","tid":1781594,"uid":293741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783c4820622a0449fba69d10b7425d9246d72b41","tid":1781594,"uid":7168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"想係商場玩捉依因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:57:52.000Z","msg":"Running man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9139660d44c2429b38b0b5a416a20176d9a4e11a","tid":1781594,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:03:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"48f18bc796f0681caf917f25f60af2c96e